    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The 6 non-assessed factors are acceptable at this model risk level per ASME V&V 40-2018 Table 1. The CFD model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device.",
